    "en": {
      "title": "Deadline for the Rajapakses",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "After January 25, President Ranil Wickremesinghe will have the opportunity to drive out the Rajapaksas, said Kumara Welkama, the leader of the New Freedom Party.",
        "Leader of Opposition Sajith Premadasa himself gave me the ticket to come to Parliament. Similarly, Sajith has also given me permission to start a new party.",
        "Kumara Welkama congratulated former President Gotabaya Rajapaksa who has returned to the country and said that he should not return to politics."
      ],
